economic growth and that offers major targets for Spanish 
industry as "lengthy and fruitful." The minister also said that 
the visit sought to boost and consolidate relations with China 
following the establishment of economic cooperation and a 
sizeable credit channel during the 1993 visit to that country by 
Prime Minister Felipe Gonzalez. 

