  [Text] Bonn -- For constitutional reasons, the Federal 
Government will not be able to provide logistic support for the 
French troops in Rwanda. This became known among government 
circles in Bonn today. It was pointed out that the German 
Government has already made available 20 million German marks 
for relief measures for the population in Rwanda. 

