<H4>    Ireland Urged To Back Sutherland </H4>

<F P=102> PM2806120894 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 28 Jun 94 p 3 
-- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM2806120894 </F>
