<H3> <TI>   Popularity Poll Shows Blair Leads Major </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Popularity Poll Shows Blair Leads Major </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2406100894 London THE TIMES in English 24 Jun 94 p 9 -- 
FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM2406100894 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


